To realistically assess the usability of LMs for KBC, we created a large-scale dataset with random facts from Wikidata, without subject restrictions to pages such as Wikipedia. One must observe that, while \ourdataset{} is an unbiased sample from Wikidata's subject set per class, it is still biased towards reality, like Wikidata itself [wikidata_bias].